latestIgtvVideos.title: HONEST REVIEWS (Part 1): @isclinical_india
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Having tried so much of skin care brands on my face, I had always wanted my own personalised skin care regime because not all of it suited my skin type and in turn creating more havoc on my face. 

Recently I came across @isclinical_india  @isclinical page and I custom made my own skin care kit. Trust me guys, I have not seen better results. 
From the cleanser to the sunscreen everything suits my face and I have zero complaints. 
You can get your customised kits according to your skin type and see the results for yourself 💯💯. 
.

latestIgtvVideos.title: Straighten you hair in the CAR with  @dyson_india
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I was so excited to try Dyson Corrale. As a person always on the go I don’t get to spend a lot of time on my hair. With a hectic schedule as mine, Dyson Corrale comes in handy and makes my life so much easier. The Corrale makes sure to gather my hair perfectly with its flexing plates technology and gives my hair 50% less damage than any other straightener ! 
It’s CORD FREE , which makes it so convenient to carry it around. 
@dyson_india You never fail to impress♥️♥️♥️
